import { Box, Button, Dialog, DialogActions, DialogContent, DialogTitle, TextField } from "@material-ui/core"
import { useState } from "react";

const Contract = () => {

    const [openDialog,setOpenDialog] = useState<boolean>(false);
    const [isEditMode,setIsEditMode] = useState<boolean>(false);

    return (
        <Box m={5}>
            
            <Button color="primary" variant="outlined" onClick={() => setOpenDialog(true)}>Add Contract</Button>

            <Dialog open={openDialog} onClose={() => {}} aria-labelledby="form-dialog-title">
                <DialogTitle id="form-dialog-title">Add Contract</DialogTitle>
                <DialogContent>
                   
                    <TextField
                        autoFocus
                        margin="dense"
                        id="name"
                        label="Email Address"
                        type="email"
                        fullWidth
                    />
                </DialogContent>
                <DialogActions>
                    <Button onClick={() => {}} color="primary">
                        {isEditMode ? 'Update' : 'Save'}
                    </Button>
                    <Button onClick={() => setOpenDialog(false)} color="primary">
                        Close
                    </Button>
                </DialogActions>
            </Dialog>


        </Box>
    )
}

export default Contract
